OL,3,CThames Water picks KKR as preferred
OL,4,Cbidder in equity rescue
OL,6,FTroubled utility Thames Water has
OL,7,Fchosen US private equity giant
OL,8,FKohlberg Kravis Roberts (KKR) as its
OL,9,Fpreferred bidder as it looks to secure
OL,10,Fa buyer to help stabilise its finances.
OL,12,FThe heavily-indebted supplier `
OL,13,FEngland's biggest water firm, with
OL,14,Fabout 16 million customers ` said KKR
OL,15,Fwould now go through to a second phase
OL,16,Fof the process to secure equity
OL,17,Finvestment.
