OL,3,CThames Water picks KKR as preferred
OL,4,Cbidder in equity rescue
OL,6,FThe supplier is hoping to finalise
OL,7,Fterms of a possible deal with KKR in
OL,8,Fthe second quarter, with aims to
OL,9,Fcomplete in the second half of the
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FBut Thames Water said there was still
OL,13,F"no certainty" over a deal, adding
OL,14,Fthat "certain senior creditors
OL,15,Fcontinue to progress in parallel
OL,16,Falternative transaction structures to
OL,17,Fseek to recapitalise the business".
