OL,3,CThames Water picks KKR as preferred
OL,4,Cbidder in equity rescue
OL,6,FThames Water said: "The company is
OL,7,Fpleased to announce that, following a
OL,8,Fdetailed assessment of proposals
OL,9,Freceived, it has taken a further step
OL,10,Fin its plan to deliver a sustainable
OL,11,Frecapitalisation by selecting KKR to
OL,12,Fenter the Phase 2 diligence stage of
OL,13,Fthe equity process as preferred
OL,14,Fpartner.
