OL,3,CThames Water picks KKR as preferred
OL,4,Cbidder in equity rescue
OL,6,F"The company remains focused on
OL,7,Fputting Thames Water on a more stable
OL,8,Ffinancial foundation, implementing its
OL,9,Fturnaround plan and delivering a
OL,10,Fmarket-led solution that is in the
OL,11,Fbest interests of customers, UK
OL,12,Ftaxpayers and the wider economy."
OL,14,FThe group's decision to proceed with
OL,15,FKKR comes after it said recently it
OL,16,Fhad received six approaches from firms
OL,17,Fto pump in investment and cash in
OL,18,Freturn for a stake in the business.
