OL,3,CThames Water picks KKR as preferred
OL,4,Cbidder in equity rescue
OL,6,FThames Water is in at least #16
OL,7,Fbillion of debt and was left on the
OL,8,Fbrink of a possible taxpayer backed
OL,9,Frescue as it was in danger of running
OL,10,Fout of cash.
OL,12,FIt recently won court approval to take
OL,13,Fout as much as #3 billion more in
OL,14,Floans, in a deal designed to keep it
OL,15,Frunning into 2026.
OL,17,FThames Water gave few details over
OL,18,FKKR's proposal, except to say it
OL,19,Fincluded a "material" reduction of its
OL,20,Fdebt and that talks were still ongoing
OL,21,Fover "other aspects of the proposal".
