OL,3,CThames Water picks KKR as preferred
OL,4,Cbidder in equity rescue
OL,6,FKKR, which is also a minority
OL,7,Fshareholder in Northumbrian Water, is
OL,8,Funderstood to have lodged a #4 billion
OL,9,Fequity bid last month in return for a
OL,10,Fmajority stake.
OL,12,FUnder its bid, KKR is believed not to
OL,13,Fbe planning to break up Thames Water
OL,14,For sell off assets to raise funds for
OL,15,Fits bid.
OL,17,FIt is also understood that Castle
OL,18,FWater, a firm co-owned by Conservative
OL,19,FParty treasurer Graham Edwards, was
OL,20,Fone of the parties that had approached
OL,21,FThames in recent months.
