OL,3,CThames Water picks KKR as preferred
OL,4,Cbidder in equity rescue
OL,6,FAnother bid came from investment group
OL,7,FCovalis, which could see the company
OL,8,Fbroken up then relisted on the stock
OL,9,Fmarket, while CK Infrastructure, part
OL,10,Fof Hong Kong's CK Hutchison group, is
OL,11,Flikewise thought to have been among
OL,12,Fthose to make approaches.
OL,14,FOn Friday, Thames Water's chief
OL,15,Ffinancial officer Alastair Cochran
OL,16,Ftold the firm he was stepping down by
OL,17,Fthe end of the month in a surprise
OL,18,Fmove given that the restructuring and
OL,19,Fsale process is not complete.
