OL,7,Fcompany, which has been at the centre
OL,8,Fof growing public anger over the state
OL,9,Fof the privatised water industry, as
OL,10,Fconsumers face steeply rising bills
OL,11,Fwhile companies pump raw sewage into
OL,12,Frivers and waterways.
